---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Industries — CA Accounting | Specialty Accounting Services"
  description="CA Accounting works with businesses in a variety of industries throughout California, with deep experience in entertainment, medical practices, and real estate."
>
  <section class="bg-cream-warm py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 fade-in">Industries</p>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-navy leading-tight mb-6 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          Areas of expertise.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-charcoal text-lg leading-relaxed fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
          CA Accounting works with businesses in a variety of industries throughout California. We have particular depth in three: entertainment, medical practices, and real estate.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom space-y-16">
      <a href="/industries/entertainment" class="group block fade-in">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-start py-12 border-t border-line hover:bg-cream-warm/50 transition-colors px-4 -mx-4 rounded">
          <div>
            <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">01</p>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy">Entertainment</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="md:col-span-2">
            <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Actors, singers, songwriters and athletes can minimize their tax burden and increase profits with our accounting and tax solutions.
            </p>
            <span class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm">Entertainment accounting →</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/industries/medical" class="group block fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-start py-12 border-t border-line hover:bg-cream-warm/50 transition-colors px-4 -mx-4 rounded">
          <div>
            <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">02</p>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy">Medical Practices</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="md:col-span-2">
            <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Doctors, dentists, chiropractors, veterinarians and other medical practitioners will benefit from our combination of practice management solutions, bookkeeping services and tax strategies.
            </p>
            <span class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm">Medical practice accounting →</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/industries/real-estate" class="group block fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-start py-12 border-t border-b border-line hover:bg-cream-warm/50 transition-colors px-4 -mx-4 rounded">
          <div>
            <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">03</p>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy">Real Estate</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="md:col-span-2">
            <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Property managers, developers, investors, brokers and agents can save time when they take advantage of our outsourced accounting services and avoid tax problems with our tax planning strategies.
            </p>
            <span class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm">Real estate accounting →</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-cream-warm py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center fade-in">
        <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">All Industries</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy mb-6">
          We work in many more.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed">
          CA Accounting works with businesses in a variety of industries throughout California, including professional service businesses like medical practices, insurance agencies and law firms, and consumer service businesses like retailers and contractors. To learn more about how we can help your business, give us a call today at 877.500.9290 to schedule a free initial consultation.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="btn-modern inline-block bg-forest text-cream font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded hover:bg-forest-hover transition-colors"
          >
            Schedule a Free Consultation
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
